{"tid":2509290,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［通識科大改］反對「過洋節」、迪士尼角色穿軍服「登島侵略，「人治不一定是負面」","createTime":"2021-04-29T10:21:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T13:03:36.000Z","uid":211994,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"52717972d5974cd46a592ed102c0e66246734a54","tid":2509290,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:21:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/COPV13JnApi/?igshid=mhkn5bya16uw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCOPV13JnApi%2F%3Figshid%3Dmhkn5bya16uw&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwX4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=a779ad37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCOPV13JnApi%2F%3Figshid%3Dmhkn5bya16uw&h=61ab6e07\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/COPV13JnApi/?igshid=mhkn5bya16uw</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210429/6ZOLG533PREO7OZICQGEM7EIUI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210429%2F6ZOLG533PREO7OZICQGEM7EIUI%2F&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwX4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=1196d8c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210429%2F6ZOLG533PREO7OZICQGEM7EIUI%2F&h=534d523e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210429/6ZOLG533PREO7OZICQGEM7EIUI/</a><br />\n<br />\n&hellip;教師用書的補充資料更引用內地學者反對「過洋節」的文章，指<strong><span class=\"gold\">非教徒「隨波逐流地認同基督教、耶誕節，無意中為基督教在中國的傳播與氾濫推波助瀾」</span></strong>，更使西方國家的軟實力在中國「不斷滲透和擴張」，呼籲「慎對耶誕節」，非教徒不要慶祝。&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ZReKnM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ZReKnM.png&h=32d938a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&hellip;書中亦引述學者指全球文化以西方文化為主導，並對外擴張的趨勢是「文化帝國主義」，<span class=\"gold\"><strong>舉例指美國跨國企業在各地間接推銷美國的價值觀，並用漫畫描繪迪士尼和麥當勞卡通人物身穿軍服登陸荒島，持槍指嚇舉手投降的民眾，問學生漫畫描繪甚麼全球化現象</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n參考答案指漫畫象徵跨國企業侵蝕發展中國家的本土文化，並將其行徑描繪成侵略，表達反文化。&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210429/TB5WD6FYGNFR7FGUSEYOONG5GI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210429%2FTB5WD6FYGNFR7FGUSEYOONG5GI%2F&d=4YJm346n2OvV5E02CjQHwX4WTS3z8ocQ7DCXl2btf88%3D&h=6dc6edd5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210429%2FTB5WD6FYGNFR7FGUSEYOONG5GI%2F&h=27811555\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210429/TB5WD6FYGNFR7FGUSEYOONG5GI/</a><br />\n<br />\n&hellip;該書「『一國兩制』下的香港」一冊建議教師問及學生看區旗與區徽時有何感受，若感光榮自豪，代表學生本地居民身份認同較高；<br />\n<br />\n奏國歌時會感動反映有愛國情懷。另建議教師提問對釣魚台被日本侵佔的感受，若學生感不開心、替國家不值等，反映其國民身份認同。&hellip;"},{"pid":"01fd2ca58e827ff11cddd9eaccdd18bc3913fa68","tid":2509290,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:23:02.000Z","msg":"漏咗一段<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;另外，該書講述行政長官選舉時，僅稱2013至2015年間，特區政府曾就2017年行政長官普選辦法進行公眾諮詢，社會未能達成共識下方案終被否決，亦隻字未提2014年佔領運動。<br />\n<br />\n有關法治基本原則部份，該書補充資料提及<span class=\"gold\"><strong>「人治不一定全是負面的」，指人治可達致實體公義，而公義亦包括情與理。</strong></span>&hellip;"},{"pid":"d99cc72420eb92235bbb32c641e67278a4b54f3b","tid":2509290,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:24:12.000Z","msg":"教科書暫時未送審<br />\n<br />\n教育局發言人回應稱，公社科課本會納入送審制度，細節有待敲定，該教材未按該科要求送審，不在「適用書目表」之內，對出版社將通識科坊間教材以公社科「課本」形式編印，「極可能會對學校或公眾造成誤會，本局深感遺憾，並會與有關出版社商榷。」"},{"pid":"ada1ca952e61b873b69436d63d37cbb2b32989b6","tid":2509290,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:49:56.000Z","msg":"本書唔寫下係釣魚台上插五星紅旗既人宜家點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"311a84211ef8e27148fea550265a4b6174c8fdcf","tid":2509290,"uid":24140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:52:26.000Z","msg":"同埋下次可以開post串支那五毛：<br />\n<br />\n身為中國人，就唔好過聖誕假復活節假"},{"pid":"612c368078ebf26ab189901f68dbfa2fc45bf5d2","tid":2509290,"uid":58387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:57:55.000Z","msg":"細路唔睇迪士尼唔通睇你喜洋洋咩。人地軟實力強，帝國主義又點咪又係大把人買"},{"pid":"58702005b45c125587b1b8a2ae31f3868fa78e41","tid":2509290,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:59:30.000Z","msg":"copyright?"},{"pid":"bd707c05baed3916d3c6707a03d4e8c254ef425d","tid":2509290,"uid":163801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T11:01:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8ZReKnM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8ZReKnM.png&h=32d938a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</blockquote><br />\n小熊維尼登陸後去咗邊？<br />\n<img src=\"https://sw.cool3c.com/user/67430/2018/a6210141-a22f-4436-be94-c9340f1a5318.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsw.cool3c.com%2Fuser%2F67430%2F2018%2Fa6210141-a22f-4436-be94-c9340f1a5318.jpg&h=307a3ea0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"35d465d584e20f215b6e88c868cd17afac8813b6","tid":2509290,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:16:34.000Z","msg":"人唔笑狗都吠啦,成本嘢低質到咁叫人愛國？唔怪得啲所謂愛國人仕無一個係高尚㗎啦!"},{"pid":"553c875666e9684ff8ec9a28eab1137b1d1e0fc4","tid":2509290,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T12:56:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e0974605dd6c5c6d6a7421cf05e660e83d05e5","tid":2509290,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T13:03:36.000Z","msg":"倒米啦<br />\n<br />\n話曬班objects都要將人治用法治包到實一實<br />\n你就攪個咁嘅topic出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"d99cc72420eb92235bbb32c641e67278a4b54f3b","tid":2509290,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:24:12.000Z","msg":"教科書暫時未送審<br />\n<br />\n教育局發言人回應稱，公社科課本會納入送審制度，細節有待敲定，該教材未按該科要求送審，不在「適用書目表」之內，對出版社將通識科坊間教材以公社科「課本」形式編印，「極可能會對學校或公眾造成誤會，本局深感遺憾，並會與有關出版社商榷。」"}}